Text.string: Tannis is a Siren? That's cool, that's cool.
Someone's gotta give those Calypso Twins a beat down, so my question to you is: are you down to beat them down?
If I ever see that Troy dude, I'm gonna knock those tattoos right off his skinny ass.
Well at least we took out one of them Calypsos. Better than nothin'!
Damn! Imagine being stranded on Nekro like that for all those years. That Typhon dude is a boss for surviving that long.
So Ava got Maya's powers, huh? That's good. Troy didn't deserve 'em, that's for sure. That's why his ass is dead.
Heard Maliwan's all over Nekro. Just can't get a break from those guys, huh?
So you found some crazy alien machine on Nekro, huh? Hope it works.
Well, if the machine doesn't work, let me pitch ya somethin'. Punching. Solves most of my problems, anyway.
Nothin' for it now but to take out Tyreen. You got this, Vault Hunter.
Pandora's been the Great Vault all along? Man, I didn't see that comin'. Granted, I wasn't really paying attention.
Time to save the world, huh?
Lilith's tough as hell. I'm sure she's all right. Wherever she is.
Hard to believe it's finally over.
Them Calypsos got what was comin' to 'em. Hell yeah.
Let's play bloody knuckles. That's where we go punch bandits till our knuckles are all bloody. It's fun!
We should lift some time. If you think you can keep up!
I like the way you fight, Vault Hunter. Whenever you wanna punch dudes, you call me up.
Hammerlock's free. Dude might talk fancy, but he can brawl. Trust me.
You're doin' some damn good work out there.
You like the B-Team logo? I think it's pretty sweet.
YOU are a grade-A badass. Just thought you should know that.
Man, I hate leg day.
Do I say “hell yeah” too much? You'd tell me, right? Hell yeah! Crap.
Hey. Where can a guy get a decent protein shake around here?
I hate killin' skags. Cute feral little bastards. But if they step to me, ain't nothin' I can do.
I was thinking about that prison break. Freedom's in my blood. And crushin' stuff. We should do it again sometime!
That Carnivora crap was crazy as hell.
Hahaha! Always love a good car chase!
Hey there!
Nice day, huh?
Another day in paradise.
I knew we could get Hammerlock outta there.
Those Calypsos just don't know when to quit, huh?
Nice job savin' Jakobs. But it's not over yet!
Hahaha! The—the “Family Jewel”. The—the... heh, hahahah! But, really, The Family Jewel? That's, just... hahahaha!
Another Vault Key fragment in the bag. Nice!
You're a Vault Hunting machine!
Hell yeah! You smacked the hell outta that Troy kid.
Gotta hand it to him, Typhon's tougher than he looks.
Can't imagine tryna raise those two brats.
Aw, man... poor Typhon, he didn't deserve that.
I knew you could do it, Vault Hunter! Hell yeah!
Did I forget leg day? Nah, I NEVER forget leg day! Ha-HA!
Man, I'm bored. Is it punch-a-clock yet? Haha, always!
You know, this place could use a garden. I'm just sayin'.
Man, back on Pandora. This planet just can't get enough Brick.
I'm hungry. I'm always hungry.
What's up?
Howdy.
I need a punch-partner.
Me and you. Punch date.
Hey. You wanna get into somethin'?
Yo.
Vault Hunter—what's good?
What's the word, VH?
Hey, Vault Hunter.
You come to workout?
It's a good day for a brawl!
I like to punch under the cover of darkness.
Need some work?
Got a thing that needs doin'.
Help me out, yeah?
You busy? 'Cause I got a thing.
Got a job here.
Hey. How's that thing comin'?
Almost done with that?
There's always another fight, am I right or am I right?
Don't you got a job to be doin'?
Doin' that thing I asked you to do?
Take your ass on, then.
All right.
Have a good one.
Go punch somethin' for me.
Good luck out there.
Later.
All right, Vault Hunter. See ya around.
See ya when I see ya.
Stay cool.
All right! I guess we're done.
